ca.uhn.hl7v2.model.v281.message

Class OSU_O41

  • java.lang.Object
    • ca.uhn.hl7v2.model.AbstractStructure
      • ca.uhn.hl7v2.model.AbstractGroup
        • ca.uhn.hl7v2.model.AbstractMessage
          • ca.uhn.hl7v2.model.v281.message.OSU_O41
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Group, Message, Structure, Visitable, Serializable

    public class OSU_O41
extends AbstractMessage

    Represents a OSU_O41 message structure (see chapter 4.4.18). This structure contains the following elements:

    • 1: MSH (Message Header)
    • 2: MSA (Message Acknowledgment)
    • 3: ERR (Error) optional repeating
    • 4: SFT (Software Segment) optional repeating
    • 5: UAC (User Authentication Credential Segment) optional
    • 6: NTE (Notes and Comments) optional repeating
    • 7: PID (Patient Identification) optional
    • 8: ARV (Access Restriction) optional repeating
    • 9: OSU_O41_ORDER_STATUS (a Group object) repeating
    See Also:
    Serialized Form
